Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're the one who doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I-I don't get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't worry about it! Let's go!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come? If the Hollow Shadow shows up...
Dialogue: 15,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anemia?
Dialogue: 15,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold still!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Senpai!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that back there?
Dialogue: 15,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get here? We're pretty deep in.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:33.24,0:00:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just jumped in headfirst when I saw you.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:36.42,0:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside—
Dialogue: 15,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a break for it!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Up you go!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:51.01,0:00:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down! I can run perfectly fine on my own!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:53.42,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Senpai!
