Dialogue: 15,0:02:36.09,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother, I love you. Big Brother, I love you.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Change your ringtone this instant.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sort of thing you'd do.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Akihito is?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Did you share information with Akkey?
Dialogue: 15,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit...
Dialogue: 15,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Without telling me?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:01.87,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let that slide, you know?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 15,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's passed.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope it has.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's making a labyrinth based on our memories?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right. Ayaka-san warned me about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She said that it usually possesses people,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but it can also create labyrinths to trap us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, where are we headed?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dunno.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.06,0:03:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How should I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If either of us knew where to go, it would be you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How am {\i1}I{\i0} supposed to know?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You came to fight without a plan?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, you didn't have a plan.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your concern!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me, anyway?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a bespectacled beauty!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:09.69,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unpleasant.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could defeat\Nthe Hollow Shadow without a plan?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My plans got skewed!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,First you show up when no one asked you to, and now you're complaining?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No one asked me?!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should have kept that story to yourself and come alone!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:28.41,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked you to look into my past or wait for me outside of my apartment, did I?!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think enticed me into all that?!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, {\i1}you{\i0} came after {\i1}me{\i0} first, Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 15,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're really getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I should be saying!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make this perfectly clear!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that I've got friends,
Dialogue: 15,0:04:58.14,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's the farthest thing from the truth!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's obvious that you do!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that I don't!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who doesn't know anything, Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:09.40,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't look!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san, I'm sorry, but I don't\Nhave the energy to carry you.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san, take off \Nyour shoes and tights!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was already—
Dialogue: 15,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san, hurry!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:37.93,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the exit!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:51.36,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the oldest tricks in the book,\Nbut if she falls for it...
Dialogue: 15,0:05:55.77,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... did we leave... my tights?
Dialogue: 15,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have anything else handy.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So who the heck was that?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sakura!"
Dialogue: 15,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you were screaming back there?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Inami Sakura.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:14.68,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the younger sister of Inami Yui, the girl I murdered.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's trying to kill you?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:24.56,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:32.24,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike Yui, Sakura's powers as an Exterminator should be near nonexistent.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So why...
Dialogue: 15,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:43.16,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The trains...
Dialogue: 15,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:13.72,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Inami Sakura!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you interfere.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the revenge crap!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:32.18,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 15,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it deceive you! That isn't the real Yui-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san, get out of there! Hurry!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Hurry! Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 15,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui is...
Dialogue: 15,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui is gone!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 15,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Hollow Shadow's main body.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:12.91,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:18.73,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of her cursed blood.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:34.42,0:09:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply touching her blood will erode your flesh, and that will be the death of you.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a reaper.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you—
Dialogue: 15,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I...
Dialogue: 15,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,look like...
Dialogue: 15,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a normal person?
Dialogue: 15,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In my eyes,
Dialogue: 15,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you are nothing more than \Na bespectacled beauty.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 15,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hollow Shadow!
Dialogue: 15,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 15,0:10:35.88,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, you're so excited, you've changed forms.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out for a quick walk.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Play with this.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:58.79,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san, hurry...
Dialogue: 15,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and stab me!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weak right now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you chase it out of my body, knowing you...
Dialogue: 15,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Senpai, you'll...
Dialogue: 15,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die. I'm immortal.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it in much longer. Hurry!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:24.86,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this... why you're here?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here because... you have do you this, right?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right, but...
Dialogue: 15,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just do it already!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating it won't change anything.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't change the blood flowing in your veins or the position your in!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't change a damn thing!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:44.47,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But... despite that, you're here!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow through with what you set out to do!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't surrender to the Hollow Shadow!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give up now, everything will have been a waste of time!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stab me!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm immortal, so...
Dialogue: 15,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 15,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,live!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spray your blood.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:46.21,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 15,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You were up against \Nthe Hollow Shadow.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't think this would happen?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't guarantee that you'll survive.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've know that Kanbara-kun is a half-demon, haven't you?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When his body is in an extremely perilous state,
Dialogue: 15,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,his demonic instincts awaken.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, dealing with him is a real headache.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 15,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cage!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's negating our supernatural powers.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:44.07,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best to regenerate the Cage.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If he starts to break it faster than I can regenerate it,
Dialogue: 15,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't be able to stop him.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If it gets to that point, \NI'll eliminate him.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate?
Dialogue: 15,0:15:55.31,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll eliminate the space encompassing\Nhis physical tissues.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:58.81,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be enough to kill him,\Nbut he can't exist that way.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:18.08,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't last much longer! Where is your big sister?
Dialogue: 15,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably on her way right now!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nino-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect this to do much!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stronger than last time!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold him! He's gonna break free!
Dialogue: 15,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-neesama?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:39.93,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I...
Dialogue: 15,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}look like...
Dialogue: 15,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a normal person?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could you possibly know how I feel?!
Dialogue: 15,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one who doesn't know anything, Kuriyama-san!
Dialogue: 15,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the same way.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 15,0:18:03.69,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, I didn't know \Nanything about you,
Dialogue: 15,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 15,0:18:11.81,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop you!
Dialogue: 15,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san?
Dialogue: 15,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I... did it again.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama-san?
Dialogue: 15,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 15,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder the Society is concerned.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll have to withdraw for now.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.73,Sign #6,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fsp-1\fay0.02\blur1\c&H3645CB&\pos(642,242)}King of Chinese Cuisine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.73,Sign #6,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fsp-1\fay0.02\blur1\pos(641,242)\c&H193D7C&}King of Chinese Cuisine
Dialogue: 15,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take your time, you know.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:25.42,0:20:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling seriously lightheaded! I need to replenish my iron.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't believe that thing wasn't the Hollow Shadow!
Dialogue: 15,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To think what I got was only worth a measly 200 yen!
Dialogue: 15,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Ayaka-san would lie to us though.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's going on here?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:43.25,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:50.18,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, aren't you going to eat that?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:54.00,0:20:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:56.93,0:20:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To the restroom.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 15,0:21:04.52,0:21:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think... I look like a normal person?
Dialogue: 15,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:14.08,0:21:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you look like a creepy \Nupperclassman with a thing for glasses.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:49.40,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}seijaku wo kirisaku you otozureta no wa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:49.40,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Breaking through the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.40,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}hitsuzen toshite no kaikou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.40,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We met in an inevitable encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:55.58,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}bokura no tame ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:55.58,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}For both our sakes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.08,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}koukai wo nageku me ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.08,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}In your mournful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:01.80,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}utsuru kimi wa sou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:01.80,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I see a reflection of regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.26,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}urei wo matotte utsukushiku saita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.26,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Enveloped in sorrow, you've blossomed beautifully
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.84,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}dare ka no seimei ni tokeru hana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.84,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}The flower that fuses into someone's life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:17.35,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}nee kimi ni mo mieru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:17.35,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Hey, do you see it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.81,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.81,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I'm sure you do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:26.61,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}kasaneta ayamachi nurikaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:26.61,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's paint over all the mistakes we've made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.24,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}nando demo ii sa kurikaeshiteiku start line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.24,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}A new start line will always be there if we want to start over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:37.96,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}kako to wa chigau asu wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:37.96,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's make our future different from the past
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.80,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}futari dake no kibou egaku start line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.80,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Our small hope will paint a new start line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:47.47,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I never say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.88,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}itsu datte sou sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.88,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}That's how I always am
Dialogue: 15,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 15,0:23:08.68,0:23:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have recovered the Hollow Shadow.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This should stall the Exterminator's Society for the time being.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:15.33,0:23:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have done well.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:17.16,0:23:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are dismissed.
